sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { FaTimes } from "react-icons/all"; import styles from './StockTableRow.css' const StockTableRow = ({ stock, onDelete }) => { const billion = 1000000000 return( onDelete(stock) }/> { stock.ticker } { stock.companyName } { stock.sector } { stock.currentPrice } { (stock.marketCap /billion).toFixed(2) } { (stock.enterpriseValue /billion).toFixed(2) } { (stock.forwardPE).toFixed(2) } { (stock.enterpriseToRev).toFixed(2) } { (stock.enterpriseToEbitda).toFixed(2) } { (stock.profitMargins).toFixed(3) } { (stock.roe).toFixed(2) } ) } export default StockTableRow
